      currently spend an estimated 8&ndash;12 hours per engagement manually creating and updating
      architecture diagrams. The tool reduces this to 1&ndash;2 hours of initial configuration, with
      subsequent updates handled automatically via SharePoint sync.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      At typical consulting day rates, this represents $1,500&ndash;$2,500 per engagement in recovered
      capacity that can be redirected to billable consulting work.
    </p>

